---
title: Creamy Tomato Soup with Pork Sausage plus Peas & Cheesy Bread
description: Have you ever had penne alla vodka and loved the sauce so much you wanted to drink it up with a straw? No? Just us? Well, that’s kind of what this creamy tomato soup is like. It’s got the added bonus of Italian sausage, bright pops of peas, and Italian seasoning to make it extra zesty. There’s also cheesy, crusty baguette to round out the meal. All this in 20 minutes? It’s not just supper, it’s souper!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-tomato-soup-with-pork-sausage-f89344fc.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/creamy-tomato-soup-with-pork-sausage-61a789fbb9e06967544df294-9d0c1041.pdf
cuisine: Italian
author: Michelle Doll Olson
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/creamy-tomato-soup-with-pork-sausage-61a789fbb9e06967544df294
nutrition:
  calories: 860 kcal
  fat: 51 g
  saturated fat: 25 g
  carbohydrates: 60 g
  sugar: 10 g
